{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"60808-my-family","title":"My Family","description":"Come and meet my big family.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Manisha Chaudhry"],"illustrators":["Rajeev Verma 'Banjara'"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/60808-my-family"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/534571/size3/9c37e0f0dfbdd4fbb5a4aada16598c88.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/534571/size6/9c37e0f0dfbdd4fbb5a4aada16598c88.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42295/size6/7bef0e9eed187cb6e47be5fe02a76b5d.jpg","text":"My name is Tuk Tuk.\nI have a large family.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42296/size6/08ae36abf079b6e0a62f55fccf9d9a95.jpg","text":"This is my mother. This is my father.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42297/size6/43e6ca9b2c60c1bdab4911ee76c8e601.jpg","text":"This is my brother Neetu and my sister Meetu is there too. Look...","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42298/size6/d1694f6c1f0b81b27b08ccdf97a9701e.jpg","text":"My grandparents have also come.\nDada-Dadi and Nana-Nani...","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42299/size6/8f71aa2df40ef8a6512567991ec7f0c7.jpg","text":"My mother has three sisters.\nThey are my ‘mausis’!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42300/size6/bcb62885ca36d202c631e0f4b75446fb.jpg","text":"My father has four brothers. Two of them are older than him and I call them ‘Tau Ji’ and two of them are younger and I call them ‘Chacha Ji’.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42301/size6/8a7a9a52ad4535e8986dab29b2e71a41.jpg","text":"There are my aunts – my two ‘Tais’ and\nmy two ‘Chachis’. See...","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42302/size6/b10c12c3059e0f309b5bb3ca76523dfb.jpg","text":"My family has five young children also.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42303/size6/3ee7e1a1c919ac7657c40b6279d6c0b2.jpg","text":"We make a lot of noise when we are all together.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42304/size6/57d97b94e97558435ae940550e539758.jpg","text":"See, what a large family I have!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42305/size6/4665bb9675035e515b8b8260ad039d4c.jpg","text":"Oh! Bujo got left out.\nHe wags his tail all day long and says...\nbow wow!! bow wow!!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":134}}